* Error Handling\nBest Practices
** Fail Fast
***_ Stop on data integrity issues
***_ Avoid corrupt data downstream
** Meaningful Logging
***_ Timestamps & record counts
***_ Error classifications
***_ No sensitive data exposure
** Recovery Planning
***_ Idempotent operations
***_ Only re-run failed tasks
***_ Repair job support
** Monitor Trends
***_ Track quality metrics over time
***_ Detect upstream system changes
** Test Failures
***_ Deliberately introduce failures
***_ Validate error handling works
@endmindmap
